metadata.name: manifesting fear
metadata.description:
"i close my eyes as i walk through the house at night, fumbling toward the first light switch - haunted by memories, fearing new ones."
-p4 (circa 2010)

story
----------------------------------------
as a kid, i'd walk through the dark house with my eyes closed til i found a light switch, out of fear of ghosts & such. we tend to see our fears manifested, be they real or not.
